<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<style>
    /* Privacy Page Styling */
.container {
  max-width: 800px;
  font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #333;
}

h2, h4 {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #212529;
}

h2 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #fe424d;
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

h4 {
  margin-top: 1.8rem;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

ul {
  padding-left: 1.2rem;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

ul li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

strong {
  color: #fe424d;
}

p {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

</style>

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>

  <p>Welcome to <strong>WonderNest</strong>. We value your trust and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data when you use our platform.</p>

  <h4 class="mt-4">1. What Information We Collect</h4>
  <p>We may collect basic personal information such as your name, email address. This helps us offer a smooth and personalized experience.</p>

  <h4 class="mt-4">2. Why We Collect It</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>To manage your bookings and listings efficiently.</li>
    <li>To enhance your overall experience on WonderNest.</li>
    <li>To send you important updates or service-related notifications.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4 class="mt-4">3. Data Protection</h4>
  <p>We use modern encryption methods and follow industry best practices to ensure your data is safe and never misused.</p>

  <h4 class="mt-4">4. Third-Party Access</h4>
  <p>We do not sell or rent your information. Data is only shared with trusted services (like secure payment providers) strictly for service fulfillment.</p>

  <h4 class="mt-4">5. Your Control</h4>
  <p>You can update or request deletion of your data by reaching out to us.
  <h4 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h4>
  <p>This Privacy Policy is a part of our commitment to transparency. We may revise it for improvements. Latest update: <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>.</p>

  
</div>
